testsuite.name: io.pivotal.extremerstartup.player.PlayerControllerTest

testcase.name: getting an invalid player id shows the no such player page
getting a player withdrawl page removes the player data
getting a valid player id shows the player data
posting to players adds a player
getting players shows the add player form
